Package: schnitr
Type: Package
Title: Modeling, Diagnostics, and Data Management
Version: 0.0.2.0
Author: Robert Schnitman <robertschnitman@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Robert Schnitman <robertschnitman@gmail.com>
Description: Family of R functions for statistical modeling, diagnostics, and data management. 
    Many of them are inspired by tidyverse's broom library. Others are simply "shortcuts" for standard procedures, 
    such as residual analysis and word frequencies.
URL: https://github.com/robertschnitman/schnitr
BugReports: https://github.com/robertschnitman/schnitr/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2), tm (>= 0.7.0), ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1), gridExtra (>= 2.3)
License: GNU General Public License v3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
